snippet.title: Ori The Collection - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Ori The Collection is now available on Nintendo Switch! Now you can own Ori and the Blind Forest Definitive Edition and Ori and the Will of the Wisps in one box with exclusive collectible art cards and digital soundtracks to both iconic games!
